               # Maintaining Serum Calcium Levels

## Analyzing Each Option:

| Hormone | Source | Primary Function |
|---------|--------|-----------------|
| **Thyroxine** | Thyroid gland | Regulates metabolism |
| **Glucagon** | Pancreas (α-cells) | Raises blood glucose |
